para_trans: New District Hospital sanctioned at Dharashiv
Government Decision No: Establishment-2023 / Q. No.127 / Health-4
Reference: - Government Decision, Public Health Department No. Establishment-2023 / Q. No. 127 / Health-4, dated 01.08.2023.
New District Hospital at Dharashiv sanctioned vide Government Decision dated 01.08.2023
The said new district hospital will have a capacity of 500 beds.
The Government decision is available on the Government of Maharashtra website www.maharashtra.gov.in.
